00:17:35,109 --> 00:17:36,230
 with a lot of vertical lines.

214
00:17:36,769 --> 00:17:39,789
 So this is the discrete time sequence

215
00:17:40,390 --> 00:17:44,690
 that represents the weekly Dow Jones index

216
00:17:44,690 --> 00:17:46,089
 over a 10-year period.

217
00:17:46,710 --> 00:17:52,029
 And here, by the way, again, is the crash of 1929.

218
00:17:53,049 --> 00:17:54,809
 It's interesting to note, by the way,

219
00:17:55,369 --> 00:17:58,410
 that actually the disaster in the stock market

