00:19:44,250 --> 00:19:50,210
 And so here you see what is the original weekly index.

244
00:19:50,210 --> 00:19:55,930
 x, and this is the result of processing that sequence with

245
00:19:55,930 --> 00:20:00,670
 an appropriate system to apply smoothing.

246
00:20:00,849 --> 00:20:03,410
 And in fact, what it is is a moving average.

247
00:20:03,789 --> 00:20:08,470
 And so here again, you can see in the smoother curve this

248
00:20:09,210 --> 00:20:12,529
 general downward trend up until this time period

